Class ViewLayer

java.lang.Object
  com.compendium.core.datamodel.PCObject
      com.compendium.core.datamodel.ViewLayer
All Implemented Interfaces:
IPCObject, ICoreConstants, java.io.Serializable
public class ViewLayer
extends PCObject
implements java.io.Serializable

The ViewLayer object holds additional information about the visual state of a JInternalFrame with a View inside. Note: This is a holding container only and does not currently write to the database

Author:
Michelle Bachler
